data.description: UNDER CONSTRUCTION! Ranch style home with finished walkout basement in the Miamisburg School District! This brand new custom built home features over 2500 sq. ft. of living space with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths! Open floor plan with cathedral ceilings, kitchen with white cabinetry, quartz countertops, large center island, subway tile backsplash, and counter bar. Oversized great room with a gas fireplace featuring a rustic beam and floor to ceiling stone surround. LVP flooring in kitchen, breakfast area, great room, entry, and baths and utility room. Master suite with walk-in closet and cathedral ceiling. The finished walkout basement includes a large rec room with patio doors, a full bath, and a 4th bedroom with a 4' x 4' egress window. 2 car garage, 16 x 12 patio, board n batten vinyl siding and stone wainscoting exterior, high efficiency gas furnace and A/C. Pictures are of same floor plan and similar finishings. All finishes must be confirmed with builder prior to writing contract. Estimated January 2024 completion.
